intent.user_query: What are the top 5 best-selling products by quantity sold?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT TOP 5 p.ProductName, SUM(oi.Quantity) AS TotalQuantitySold FROM fitness_db.Products p JOIN fitness_db.OrderItems oi ON p.ProductID = oi.ProductID GROUP BY p.ProductName ORDER BY TotalQuantitySold DESC;

arguments.sql: SELECT TOP 5 p.ProductName, SUM(oi.Quantity) AS TotalQuantitySold FROM fitness_db.Products p JOIN fitness_db.OrderItems oi ON p.ProductID = oi.ProductID GROUP BY p.ProductName ORDER BY TotalQuantitySold DESC;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
